<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index Closes Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, August 1 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange closed at 1,708.62 on Sunday, up 7.19 points from
Saturday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 959,820 shares changed hands in 869 turns and the
turnover was 2.95 billion rials (about 983,000 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
During the trading session, shares of 34 companies made gains
while those of seven others declined. 
