<HEADLINE> Guangzhou TV Presents Programs to Macao Viewers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, August 2 (Xinhua) -- In the coming month, television
viewers in Macao will have the opportunity to watch TV programs
from Guangzhou, a major city in south China.
</P>
<P>
Presented by the Guangzhou Television Station, the programs
include TV play series, artistic performances, children plays and
scenery documentaries.
</P>
<P>
All the programs have been broadcast by Guangzhou TV before,
and they add up to a total length of 23 hours.
</P>
