<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 2 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan Monday strongly
rebutted reports that it has received some formula from the United
States to open up the Line of Control (LoC) to allow the free
movement of Kashmiris across it.
</P>
<P>
"We have received no proposal from the United States till
today," said Foreign Office spokesman Tariq Altaf here.
</P>
<P>
