formula to Pakistan and India to allow more freedom to the
governments in the two parts of Kashmir separately controlled by
them.
</P>
<P>
Under this formula, the reports said, the Kashmiris will be
allowed to travel across the border freely and there will be
elections in both parts of Kashmir in five years.
</P>
<P>
The representatives of the Kashmiris elected under these polls
would decide the future of the disputed area, according to the
reports. 
