hatred. The culprits will be found and brought to justice,"
Prikhodko quoted Yeltsin as saying.
</P>
<P>
Barak, for his part, praised Russia's role as a co-sponsor of
the Middle East peace process, urging Moscow to exert its
influence on the Arab countries in the region to make the talks on
a peace settlement constructive and business-like.
</P>
<P>
Barak, who arrived here early Monday on a one-day visit, will
also meet Russian Prime Minister Sergei Stepashin, Foreign
Minister Igor Ivanov and leaders of the Jewish community. 
