million Australian dollars (573 million U.S. dollars), with
falling stocks outnumbering rising stocks 746 to 474 and 384
stocks remaining steady.
</P>
<P>
The all industrials index retreated 53.2 points to 5,200, while
the all resources index stacked on 14.2 to 1,273.5 points.
</P>
<P>
Bank sector heavyweight National Australia Bank slipped 31
cents to 23.09 Australian dollars, Commonwealth Bank dipped 24
cents to 23.88 Australian dollars, ANZ drifted eight cents to
10.70 Australian dollars and Westpac lost 3.6 cents to 9.90
Australian dollars. 
