<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 1 (Xinhua) -- The U.S. Tennis Association
has selected Stanford University's Taube Family Tennis Stadium of
California for the Fed Cup final between the United States and
Russia on September 18-19.
</P>
<P>
