international women's team tournament was made Sunday during the
final of the Bank of the West Classic, a women's tour event held
at Stanford.
</P>
<P>
The Fed Cup final will be two singles matches September 18,
followed by two singles and a doubles match the following day.
</P>
<P>
The United States has won the Fed Cup 15 times since its
inception in 1963. The U.S. team, headed by sisters Venus and
Serena Williams, overwhelmed Italy in the semi-finals in late July.
Russia eliminated Slovakia in the other semi-final. 
